@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: PDF Tools Operations
actor User
participant "UI (MergePdfActivity/SplitPdfActivity/PdfConvertActivity)" as UI
participant "PdfService" as Service
participant "CloudConvertService" as CloudConvert
participant "Local Storage" as Storage

== Merge PDFs ==
User -> UI : Select multiple PDFs, click Merge
UI -> Service : mergePdfs(uriList)
activate Service
Service -> Storage : read input PDFs
Storage --> Service : PDF streams
Service -> Service : combine pages
Service -> Storage : save merged PDF
Storage --> Service : new PDF URI
Service --> UI : Success
deactivate Service
UI --> User : Show merged file

== Convert Document to PDF ==
User -> UI : Select Doc/Image, click Convert
UI -> Service : convertToPdf(uri)
activate Service
Service -> CloudConvert : send file and format
activate CloudConvert
CloudConvert --> Service : Return generated PDF stream
deactivate CloudConvert
Service -> Storage : save PDF
Storage --> Service : new PDF URI
Service --> UI : Success
deactivate Service
UI --> User : Show converted file
@enduml
